{"_path":"/maps/_devops/devops","_dir":"_devops","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"DevOps","description":"DevOps 是一种开发理论，它致力于将大量自动化操作整合进开发到交付过程中，以消除各个团队之间的隔阂，使需求尽快交付，并得到质量反馈。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"DevOps","src":"https://mgear-image.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/image/other/20220627182016.png?w=60"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"子领域"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"子领域"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_devops/version-control/version-control"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"版本控制"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Git、版本管理与工作流"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_devops/cicd/cicd"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CI/CD"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 持续集成与持续部署"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_devops/container/docker"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"容器"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Docker 容器技术"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_devops/logging/rotatelogs"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"日志"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 日志轮转与管理"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"概述"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"概述"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DevOps 是一套实践、工具和文化理念的组合，旨在缩短系统开发生命周期，同时持续交付高质量的软件。它强调开发（Development）和运维（Operations）团队之间的协作与沟通，通过自动化流程来实现更快的交付和更稳定的系统运行。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"DevOps 的核心理念包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"持续集成/持续部署（CI/CD）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：自动化构建、测试和部署流程"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基础设施即代码（IaC）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：使用代码管理和配置基础设施"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"监控与日志"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：实时监控系统状态，收集和分析日志"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"版本控制"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：追踪代码变更，支持协作开发"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自动化测试"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：确保代码质量，减少人工错误"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过这些实践，DevOps 帮助团队实现更频繁的发布、更低的故障率和更快的恢复时间。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"子领域","depth":2,"text":"子领域"},{"id":"概述","depth":2,"text":"概述"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_devops:devops.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_devops/devops.md","_stem":"6.maps/_devops/devops","_extension":"md"}